# Kanban Board UI

## Objective
Build the visual layout of the Kanban board ("Quest Board").

## Tasks
1. Create column components for each quest status.
2. Create quest card components displaying title, bounty XP, and difficulty.
3. Fetch data from `KanbanDataLayer` and populate the columns.
4. Apply consistent RPG/dark-mode styling.
